oper.", "What you need to know before you even think about becoming a Web Developer", "Alright then, after giving it much thought you have decided and are hell bent on becoming the next “Batman” of Web Development. ", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "74-revision-v1", "", "", "2018-03-15 18:07:40", "2018-03-15 18:07:40", "", "74", "http://localhost:8888/2018/03/15/74-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
